				<a href="//lens.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/11/12/nov-12-2015-pictures-of-the-day/" rel="bookmark"
				   title="Permanent Link to Nov. 12, 2015 â Pictures of the Day">
					Nov. 12, 2015 â Pictures of the Day				</a>
